---
description: AI safety rules
alwaysApply: true
---
- Image goes ONLY to trait extraction (1st prompt). Candidate (2nd) and judge (3rd) prompts are TEXT ONLY.
- No face recognition, identity matching, biometrics, embeddings, or exact-lookalike claims — in code, prompts, or UI copy.
- Validate every Gemini response with Zod; reject unsafe wording (shared FORBIDDEN_RESULT_PHRASES).
- GEMINI_MODEL from .env only. Prompts loaded from files via PromptLoaderService — never inline in services.
- Results framed as playful style/vibe game; disclaimer always shown.
